00:07:08.400 --> 00:07:13.280
Whip gets there just in time to get him off her.&nbsp;
He offers the man some money and brings Nicole&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:13.280 --> 00:07:18.960
to his farmhouse after realising she has nowhere&nbsp;
to go. That night, the two end up having sex. 
&nbsp;

00:07:19.840 --> 00:07:24.960
