to control himself but is unsuccessful. 
&nbsp;

00:09:50.160 --> 00:09:54.400
The following day is the day of the&nbsp;
hearing. Charlie and Hugh knock on his door.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:54.400 --> 00:09:59.520
When Whip doesn’t open it, they walk inside using&nbsp;
an extra set of keys. They are shocked to find the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:59.520 --> 00:10:05.040
