to call Harling and bring him some cocaine.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:10.400 --> 00:10:14.560
Charlie and Hugh have no other way to get&nbsp;
Whip back to his senses before the hearing,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:14.560 --> 00:10:20.640
so they agree. Harling comes to the hotel room&nbsp;
and snorts cocaine along with Whip. Whip then&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:20.640 --> 00:10:26.240
gets ready and leaves the hotel confidently. 
